===Conjunction===
#"'''Because'''" is used to add a reason to a statement.

===Synonyms===
* [[Therefore]]
* [[Since]] (''note'' : this word, contrary to because, has several meanings) 
* [[For]] (''note'' : this word, contrary to because, has several meanings) 

